  "title": "Warehouse Export Coordinator (East) $2500",
  "description": "<p><strong>Support Export department: </strong><br /><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>1)    Preparing documents such as (Labels, invoice,packing list & workfile) which is supply by customer to warehouse for labeling purpose.</p><p>2)    Execution of awb namely as House Airway Bill & Master Airway Bill for shipment to be export out.</p><p>3)    Ensure that all documentation are in order to meet the airline and custom requirement.</p><p>4)    Coordinate with appointed Contractor on the launching-in of our daily Export cargo and documents.</p><p>5)    To monitor the status daily shipment via Airline Website and update to our Nippon Oversea Office.</p><p>6)    Reports to monitor / update daily.</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 years’ experience in the supply chain industry</li><li>Able to work within tight deadlines</li><li>Proficient in MS Office</li></ul><p><u><strong>Other Info</strong></u>\nWorking Location:      Alps (Transport pickup at Tampines and Tanah Merah)\nWorking hours: 5.25 days (Rotating\nShift)      </p><p>1)      1300hrs - 2230hrs  </p><p>2)      1600hrs - 0130hrs\n</p>",
